from north america or europe but focuses instead on arab north 
africa and black west africa where many countries are former 
french colonies or protectorates 
a survey of 926 people conducted by the polling service bva 
showed 68 percent of the french think the level of tolerance has 
been reached for immigration and 50 percent oppose the 
construction of new mosques 
