here last year production was 60 percent to 70 percent below 
normal 
for larry richard a 36yearold father of three who farms 1000 
acres near the town of horace 39000 in aid even coupled with 
55000 in crop insurance amounted to just enough to break even 
we were able to cover all our bills thats all i had really hoped 
for 
if that seems like a lot richard who grows wheat soybeans and 
