phelps dodge corp says it will take pretax 
charges of about 375 million in the fourth quarter to write down 
the value of certain assets that have been idle for several years 
after deferred tax benefits these charges will reduce net 
income in the quarter by about 250 million or 7 per common 
share the copper company said wednesday adding it still expected 
